title: The Mayor of Casterbridge (2003) TV
description:
Another Thomas Hardy tragedy, like Tess of the D'Urbervilles, uploaded earlier,
are both depressing in their greatness. I prefer happy endings.

Nevertheless it is a very good movie.

I thought I had come across this torrent on Mininova and Pirate Bay, but today
I could not locate it anywhere. If I'm repeating what has gone before, pardon.

Details on the storyline are in the Word .doc attached.


I'm also ready to upload The Way We Live Now.
But after getting it all prepared, I found it was already available,
but not too supported. Maybe I'll send mine later.
